to stop this fight,

374
00:20:37,139 --> 00:20:38,873
before he attacks in earnest.

375
00:20:38,906 --> 00:20:40,839
Otherwise, Ichigo will be--

376
00:20:45,073 --> 00:20:46,506
-Very well.

377
00:20:46,539 --> 00:20:48,373
Obviously, you have
improved even more

378
00:20:48,406 --> 00:20:51,173
than I would have
thought possible.

379
00:20:51,206 --> 00:20:52,773
So you leave me no choice.

380
00:20:52,806 --> 00:20:54,973
Before you become
too full of yourself,

381
00:20:55,006 --> 00:20:57,573
I shall show you the
difference between us.

382
00:20:57,606 --> 00:20:58,073
-Uh.

383
00:21:00,873 --> 00:21:03,873
-The gap in power you
could never hope to bridge,

384
00:21:03,906 --> 00:21:07,573
not even if you had
1,000 years of training.

